Text: A lovely FZ gift. Thank you Pete. Vale Demonoid.

I am seeding this non-stop - no peers shown.  I can contact Admin and ask them to delete, I'll re-up, or, try downloading the torrent again to see if it kicks off.  

Shellsunder - I am envious of you meeting FZ - I consider him to be my "hero" - Unique, unafraid to go against the norm, and endlessly creative.  He is, IMHO, one of the most misunderstood and underappreciated artists of the current age.  

I have a huge selection of FZ videos and Albums (CDs), I will work on uploading these.  Feel free to contact me directly.  

Cheers.
